        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e84bd44a-f4d4-41be-bd93-32582e88c83c">
                Mr. Baxter
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e84bd44a-f4d4-41be-bd93-32582e88c83c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-01-28/debates/b729eac8-7b54-4797-a8e8-9d56ef76cdea/MotionOfConfidenceInHisMajestySGovernment#contribution-e84bd44a-f4d4-41be-bd93-32582e88c83c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">If my hon. Friend and accomplice had let me finish my sentence, he would have heard me say that the Prime Minister and the Government had been subjected to very harsh criticism in this House and in the newspapers, and that it was entirely correct.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e84bd44a-f4d4-41be-bd93-32582e88c83c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-01-28/debates/b729eac8-7b54-4797-a8e8-9d56ef76cdea/MotionOfConfidenceInHisMajestySGovernment#contribution-e84bd44a-f4d4-41be-bd93-32582e88c83c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-e2e3e362-6761-4b01-9dde-6ba2fd52b014">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-e2e3e362-6761-4b01-9dde-6ba2fd52b014">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
