    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On a point of Order, Mr. Speaker. May I ask whether these remarks have any relevance to the Motion which this House is now discussing?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bdab12e1-d55b-4c45-95fd-f1ff7d23c220" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-01-28/debates/b729eac8-7b54-4797-a8e8-9d56ef76cdea/MotionOfConfidenceInHisMajestySGovernment#contribution-bdab12e1-d55b-4c45-95fd-f1ff7d23c220">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

