                Commander Bower
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-48641295-4939-48c4-91ed-e143a4ce5655" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-01-28/debates/b729eac8-7b54-4797-a8e8-9d56ef76cdea/MotionOfConfidenceInHisMajestySGovernment#contribution-48641295-4939-48c4-91ed-e143a4ce5655">
